<div class="admin-section-header">
    <h2>캠핑 주문 확인</h2>
    <p>비회원 주문의 수령희망일자, 수령지, 일요일/연휴 안내 여부를 재차 검증합니다.</p>
</div>

<table class="admin-table">
    <thead>
        <tr>
            <th>주문번호</th>
            <th>주문자</th>
            <th>수령희망일자</th>
            <th>수령지</th>
            <th>주소</th>
            <th>검증상태</th>
            <th>요청사항</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
        <% if (orders && orders.length) { %>
            <% orders.forEach(order => { %>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong><%= order.order_number %></strong></td>
                    <td>
                        <%= order.customer_name %><br>
                        <small><%= order.customer_phone %></small>
                    </td>
                    <td><%= order.requested_receive_date %></td>
                    <td>
                        <%= order.destination_type === 'campground' ? '캠핑장' : '배송지' %>
                        <% if (order.holiday_warning) { %>
                            <br><span class="status-badge incoming">재확인 필요</span>
                        <% } %>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <% if (order.campground_name) { %>
                            <strong><%= order.campground_name %></strong><br>
                        <% } %>
                        <%= order.delivery_address %>
                        <% if (order.delivery_detail) { %>
                            <br><small><%= order.delivery_detail %></small>
                        <% } %>
                        <% if (order.holiday_warning_reason) { %>
                            <br><small class="text-red"><%= order.holiday_warning_reason %></small>
                        <% } %>
                    </td>
                    <td><span class="status-badge <%= order.verification_status === 'need_check' ? 'out' : 'stock' %>"><%= order.verification_status %></span></td>
                    <td><%= order.customer_memo || '-' %></td>
                </tr>
            <% }) %>
        <% } else { %>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="7" class="text-center">접수된 캠핑 주문이 없습니다.</td>
            </tr>
        <% } %>
    </tbody>
</table>

<style>
.admin-section-header {
    margin-bottom: 18px;
}
.admin-section-header h2 {
    margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.admin-section-header p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #777;
}
.text-red {
    color: #c0392b;
}
</style>
